name: Fenton
content:
Fenton was a male Gungan smuggler who lived in Kaadara during the Galactic Civil War.
Fenton was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Fenton was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
